I generally like the concept here and feel like something really fun could be built on it, but I have two specific issues that have caused me to give this a -1. One issue is that the dialog doesn't really read to me the way people would naturally speak to each other and comes off as very script-y - I think if you give it a read out loud you may feel the same way. The other is that, as a person who deals with medical correspondence daily, I am unable to believe that a physician would not only write things that are  and sign them, leaving open the possibility of those words being used against them, but also that they would do so on facility letterhead. Fixing those two would go a long way towards turning my opinion to the positive, but I am only one person with one person's opinions so take or leave them as you like. Thanks for sharing your writing with us!







